title: विद्युत तारांवर चालणारा तो लाईनमन कोकणातील नाही; हा व्हिडियो तेलंगणामधील
author: marathi.factcrescendo.com
vclaim:
A youth in #Telangana walked on the suspended high-tension wires to remove a tree branch that was tripping the power supply.



The incident occurred on Monday in #Nizampur in Sadashivpet mandal of Sangareddy district, about 75 km from #Hyderabad.
